      <odd id="aspace_6fa706221b2c456ea3947a3de543b212">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 46-B (YRG 46-B), Records and materials documenting individual Yale buildings, facilities, and grounds.</p>  
      </odd>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_fd6444454eda141eee666669386e01a1">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>Access to the records is partially restricted. See Collection Contents for details.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <separatedmaterial id="aspace_ed0e7ff70409cd1f6786dd7fa7374aa2">
         <head>Separated Materials</head>
         <p>Architectural drawings transferred to Record Unit 1, Architectural drawings and maps of Yale University buildings and grounds, Series II, boxes 659, 672-677, 688-694, 722, 726-731.</p>  
      </separatedmaterial>
      <prefercite id="aspace_27567f80011d876b7d08d5fc2ff1a056">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Yale University Library Records Concerning the Construction of the Irving S. Gilmore Music Library (RU 270). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <arrangement id="aspace_2967bbcbacbaca49e714f9687be72048">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged in one series: I. Construction Documents, 1995; and subsequent accessions.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_2cb9d86f5394001ccad25459def563a4">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of architectural drawings, sketches, photographs, floor plans, bid addenda, and related construction and renovation records documenting the design and construction of the Irving S. Gilmore Music Library at Yale.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
